The paper discusses the use of Deep Learning techniques to solve various computer security challenges, which falls under the category of "Computer Security and Cryptography" (cs.CR). The paper also extensively discusses the use of machine learning algorithms, which falls under the category of "Machine Learning" (cs.LG). Additionally, the paper discusses the use of Artificial Intelligence techniques, which falls under the category of "Artificial Intelligence" (cs.AI). The paper also discusses the use of software engineering techniques to solve security challenges, which falls under the category of "Software Engineering" (cs.SE). Finally, the paper discusses the use of system-level techniques to solve security challenges, which falls under the category of "Systems and Control" (cs.SI).
